MobileStack boilerplate License Agreement

TL;DR;

Personal License: Build unlimited projects as an individual.

Team License: Build unlimited projects as a team.

This License Agreement ("Agreement") is entered into between MobileStack, whose contact information is brahyam@getmobilestack.com, and you, the user ("Licensee"), regarding the use of the MobileStack coding boilerplate (the "Product") available at https://getmobilestack.com/ (the "Website"). By downloading, accessing, or using the Product, Licensee agrees to be bound by the terms and conditions of this Agreement.

1. Grant of License

1.1 Personal License

Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, MobileStack grants Licensee a non-exclusive, non-transferable, and non-sublicensable Personal License to use the MobileStack coding boilerplate for the following purposes:

Create unlimited projects.

Build and develop mobile applications for personal use or commercial use.

1.2 Team License

Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, MobileStack grants Licensee a non-exclusive, non-transferable, and non-sublicensable Team License to use the MobileStack coding boilerplate for the following purposes:

Create unlimited projects.

Build and develop mobile applicationsas part of a team.

Share the code with other members of the team.

